{"tid":1443555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[曱甴論]利用對家嘅無知為我哋創造優勢","createTime":"2019-08-11T09:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:07:41.000Z","uid":291898,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9a02b8c0df23865052c7800e7c3e1cdb7786c4","tid":1443555,"uid":291898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"「曱甴」一詞嘅由來<br />\n1994年---盧旺達大屠殺<br />\n為了令胡圖族人仇視圖西族人，政權大力鼓吹胡圖族優等論，把圖西族人貶稱為「蟑螂」，並且大肆渲染圖西族人處心積累要征服胡圖族的輿論，使得胡圖族人憤起屠殺圖西族人。<br />\n<br />\nWW2---納粹德國<br />\n日耳曼人被納粹認為是雅利安人種中最為純正者，由此即為優等人種。猶太人及其他不適宜的人種被認定為雅利安人的敵人，滲透到德國社會當中，剝削和壓迫雅利安人，因而受到迫害並遭屠殺。猶太人當初被稱為「老鼠」，後被稱為「曱甴」，其他非雅利安人，如波蘭人則被稱為「東歐品種的曱甴」(an East European species of cockroach)。<br />\n<br />\n去人性化(DEHUMANIZATION)<br />\n即以低等生物或物件去標籤、貶低、物化他人，讓施暴者合理化自身暴行，使其不受良心譴責。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班黑警同藍絲就係以「曱甴」標籤抗爭者，合理化佢哋嘅暴行，包括對女抗者甚至女路人使用性暴力、行使過度武力等等。另一方面以「為法治而戰」、「正義」之師包裝自己，洗班黑警腦，令佢哋以為自己真係為正義以戰，從而對抗爭者心生仇恨，務求趕盡殺絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候文宣同外國巴絲就要出動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋要收集班前線汪汪叫抗爭者「曱甴」嘅短片整合同埋翻譯香港警察佐級協會稱呼抗爭者為「曱甴」嘅公開聲明，將佢貼到全球都係，將佢推到有領事館關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你仆街啦黑警"},{"pid":"212de7f44420a71e7757b8bcbfc2dcbc93cf5c7e","tid":1443555,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港警察，賤過甴曱</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6020e8431d305bdc6331ada645de24ace09bf3ee","tid":1443555,"uid":183631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"曱甴警察，社會垃圾！！<br />\n過街老鼠，人人喊打！！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"d93cd7ed8e4c9eeb3c139a93f382939096264ee9","tid":1443555,"uid":183631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"曱甴警察，社會垃圾！！<br />\n過街老鼠，人人喊打！！<strong><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></strong></strong></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"95d274c80a928b2444fcaca793bda6f647863640","tid":1443555,"uid":183631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"曱甴警察，社會垃圾！！<br />\n過街老鼠，人人喊打！！"},{"pid":"7ba6e4128cefeaf0163a4e8231bc76f36852ad18","tid":1443555,"uid":225985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10534666f1917e10a595a1aa1c8918592053537d","tid":1443555,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"曱甴警察，社會垃圾！！<br />\n過街老鼠，人人喊打！！"},{"pid":"cb314a599d1053f10047139bc7cadc11fcdcf3ae","tid":1443555,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"想搞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>快閃連儂牆</strong></span></span>，有興趣可以入黎一齊傾<br />\n<br />\n連儂場!進!化!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433384\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433384</a>"},{"pid":"f9dd59f71e6cc354e424d27625738e85398f2032","tid":1443555,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993f4b354dd0c047a9af54179d84e6d98884fc37","tid":1443555,"uid":261330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢地稱我為甲由係好嚴重的事,因為好似納粹主義者對待猶太人甘，佢哋唔會再視我地為個體，而係一堆野，將我地量化，所以就算我地有人死左，都唔會覺得有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5263bb9b36c780f8ecdcb07a1ace38fdc61da3d7","tid":1443555,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"文宣煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=